POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (20): WPV1 ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS MOZAMBIQUE, CVDPV2 ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS (CHAD, MOZAMBIQUE, NIGER, NIGERIA, TOGO) COMMENT
